text: The Game and Feral Animal Control Act 2002 is an act to manage and regulate the hunting of game in New South Wales in Australia. The Act established the Game Council New South Wales. ==See also== *Hunting in Australia ==References== ==External links== *Game and Feral Animal Control Act 2002 at the New South Wales Government Category:Hunting in Australia Category:New South Wales legislation Category:2002 in Australian law Category:2002 in the environment Category:2000s in New South Wales
